title: Language Arts, Reading Practice Test 1
intro_text:
Language Arts, Reading

Welcome to the Language Arts, Reading Practice Test.

There are 20 questions. The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the GRE® exam and to give you a study plan for what you need to brush up on for the test.

If you are unsure of an answer, click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later. There are four versions of the Language Arts, Reading Practice Test. You will be able to retake the tests as often as you choose.
